  "text": "The use and care of animals used in this study followed the guidelines of the NIH Animal Research Advisory Committee. C57BL/6 mice were obtained from NCI-Frederick (Frederick, MD) and EIIa-Cre mice were obtained from The Jackson Laboratories (Bar Harbor, ME). All protocols were approved by the National Cancer Institute-Center for Cancer Research Animal Care and Use Committee (protocol numbers EIB-076 and EIB-094). Rabbit SNAP-23 antibody is described in a previous publication [CITATION_1] . Syntaxin 1a (HPC 1; Wako chemicals), syntaxin 3 (Alomone labs), syntaxin 13 (15G2, Abcam), VAMP-2 (Cl 69.1; Synaptic Systems), a-tubulin (Sigma) antibodies were purchased from commercial sources as indicated.",
